headline: Totino’s™ Pizza Rolls™ Brings Back Fan-Favorite Intergalactic Friend Chazmo in Broadway-Inspired "CHAZMO: The Musical" Ahead of the Big Game

headline: Patagonia Urges Lawmakers to Vote Against Further ICE Funding
summary: The outdoor apparel company, known for its environmental and political advocacy efforts, sent letters this week to senators in California, Colorado, Virginia and other states.
